title: Colin Cowherd's Blazing 5: 01/12/2019

description:
Colin does a Blazing 5 for the divisional round of the playoffs after going 4-0 on his unofficial picks last weekend.  RJ Bell of Pregame.com and Fox Sports Radio tells him which picks the wise guys in Vegas agree and disagree with in this exclusive podcast
